query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('.net-assembly',
'android-imageview',
'autofac',
'core-location',
'django-queryset',
'forms-authentication',
'log4j2',
'pom.xml',
'spark-dataframe',
'sql-injection',
'system',
'uialertview',
'vuex',
'xdebug',
'xmpp');
